{"tid":516814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2018飲到鳩曬，條女怒屌失禮","createTime":"2018-01-01T17:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T19:13:42.000Z","uid":32835,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbe53bbbaf082328f0ceb9b3cb0b6a010ed60b5","tid":516814,"uid":32835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"琴晚飲大左，情緒大崩潰。所有積積埋埋嘅嘢一次過爆曬出嚟。初頭就喊到憨鳩，然後就鳩嗌。無啦啦就扯火屌鳩路人，踢嘢。之後就坐低左同個朋友講人生。今日斷曬片，俾條女屌到憨鳩。<br />\n<br />\n雖然知道飲酒應該適可而止，亦明白要有酒品。但當醉左控制唔到自己嘅時候點算，第二朝仲斷片。我點樣可以應承女女唔會再飲完發酒癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcafaad77df9a9452a89469e4566592950a1aab","tid":516814,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"慢慢飲啦 傻系 真係人出酒你出命咩"},{"pid":"bbaabf5fa0b855ac5c4f5bb70ee7dd95a300e972","tid":516814,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8c4a8e7fe1877a1efce140d154d6f7dca96230","tid":516814,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:34:51.000Z","msg":"最憎on9無酒品<br />\n利申斷過一次片只係訓死左"},{"pid":"c7961c4dc93bd7c90d6f0a8b1a7a1271cc5f6fbc","tid":516814,"uid":32835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:11:45.000Z","msg":"同佢講話改，佢話你都醉左仲點控制到。<br />\n唉佢又講得啱"},{"pid":"de02db67262d971969d04a3d5be7d5701af425aa","tid":516814,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:13:42.000Z","msg":"戒酒"}]}